    "This scale produces a score for each of the defined symptoms for medical personnel, being emotional exhaustion, depersonalization, and personal accomplishment using items such as, \"I feel emotionally drained from my work, \" \"I have accomplished many worthwhile things in this job, \" and \"I do not really care what happens to some patients. \""
